    "title": "Polling Preparations Intensify Across Dharmapuri",
    "summary": "Authorities across Dharmapuri district have significantly intensified preparations for the upcoming polling day, ensuring that all logistical, administrative, and security arrangements are fully in place. Polling booths across rural and urban regions have been equipped with Electronic Voting Machines (EVMs), VVPAT units, drinking water facilities, shaded waiting areas, and accessibility provisions for elderly and differently-abled voters. Officials conducted multiple inspections and coordination meetings to ensure seamless execution. Special focus has been given to remote villages to ensure inclusive participation and accessibility."
